      "message": "[🟡 Suggestion] Line 86: The subscription buffers same-account auth events before operationId is known, but it never handles addDevice returning 0 or another invalid operation id. In that case operationId remains 0 and the observer will keep appending future auth results for the account indefinitely. Check the returned operation id immediately and dispose/reset state on failure.\n```suggestion\nlet newOperationId \u003d self.accountService.addDevice(accountId: account.id, token: jamiAuthentication)\nguard newOperationId !\u003d 0 else {\n    authOperationDisposable.disposable \u003d Disposables.create()\n    pendingAuthResults.removeAll()\n    withAnimation { exportState \u003d .error }\n    return\n}\noperationId \u003d newOperationId\n```",
